      <div class="service-card__details">
        <ul>
          <li>The Virginia Chapter of ABC is a statewide, pro-business association representing construction and construction-related firms, with offices in Chantilly, Richmond, and Hampton Roads. ABC-VA has the compelling distinction of being the only association that is based on a philosophy of free enterprise.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card__side service-card__side--back">
      <%= link_to root_path, class: "btn btn--md" do %>
        <%= content_tag(:span, "Service Details") %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  
